data.description: "Get ready to downsize your worries and upgrade your life with this ridiculously adorable tiny house! It is so cute and compact, but has all the amenities needed. 430 sq ft with one bedroom and 1 bath. Upgraded kitchen, with quartz counter tops, and stainless-steel appliances, new paint inside, with new wood laminate flooring. Good sized yard at 6,350 sq ft. new side fences and brand-new sod and sprinklers out front. Get ready to make a splash – your dream pool is on the brink of becoming the centerpiece of your ultimate outdoor escape! The pool is so close to being complete, all it needs is plaster and all the brand-new equipment has been purchased and needing installation. New cement and cement patio were completed. This could really be a great yard with a little bit of work and your imagination! Just a few minutes’ walk to downtown Redlands, all amenities and easy freeway access. It's the kind of place where you can't help but say 'aww' every time you walk through the door. If happiness came in square footage, this place would be a mansion!"
